** ARE YOU POWERING THE NEXT
WAVE OF MARITIME INNOVATION?
------------------------------------------------------------

The maritime and industrial sectors are evolving at an unprecedented pace—with innovation, sustainability, and digital transformation at the helm.

The Oceanus Awards 2025 honour outstanding organisations and individuals who are redefining maritime excellence across Asia and beyond. From port and vessel technology to marine engineering, green shipping, and smart logistics, this is your chance to shine.
